 Handling the form submission
form.addEventListener("submit", async (e) => {
  e.preventDefault();

 Explanation:

When the user clicks “Add Product”, this event listener runs.

e.preventDefault() stops the form from doing its default behavior (which would reload the page).

We handle the submission using JavaScript (AJAX) instead.

